{"tid":2108762,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"聖靈真係乜都識","createTime":"2020-07-14T19:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T16:54:49.000Z","uid":222614,"like":10,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"80298309cf80f8d4681773f602b3c0079b1c24b5","tid":2108762,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:02:18.000Z","msg":"有時個腦實左，情況危急又唔知點<br />\n<br />\n聖靈就會畀指示我，係我思想入面提點我，話我知發生咩問題<br />\n<br />\n然後我跟住做，果然解決到問題<br />\n<br />\n已經發生過好多次，今日又有經歷<br />\n<br />\n我份人本身容易緊張同亂黎，試過無數次搞到一獲泡<br />\n<br />\n但學識遵從聖靈嘅指示後，每次遇到問題都會順利解決<br />\n<br />\n有聖靈嘅人會知我講咩<br />\n<br />\n願榮歸基督耶穌，amen!"},{"pid":"3a87710126b9889299e40745020cdc0c4f92318c","tid":2108762,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:05:41.000Z","msg":"聖靈係耶穌嘅恩賜，同學們一齊歸榮耀畀耶穌我地嘅神！"},{"pid":"88cdd94a4fcbe41ac9fae0b0c970823080e6ba4a","tid":2108762,"uid":305631,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:08:19.000Z","msg":"多謝你嘅分享"},{"pid":"be8eea4abd55065eb8115df252c43f7aead24cb5","tid":2108762,"uid":287040,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:08:19.000Z","msg":"AMEN <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝神<br />\n唱返首主能夠先<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9_tIPgNjBS0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9_tIPgNjBS0&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=8c55e917\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9_tIPgNjBS0</a>"},{"pid":"e490cd6b84b5ba9895d05e797ce315daae11c93e","tid":2108762,"uid":39326,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:11:46.000Z","msg":"聖靈乜都識會唔會犯國安法?"},{"pid":"b62b073fa9cc25f7afccc348573a917e88861103","tid":2108762,"uid":343268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:12:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c61fee46c74aa244de2d90a7f46cee5f3639b444","tid":2108762,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:14:21.000Z","msg":"願基督耶穌嘅榮光充滿全地，及至世界每個角落！"},{"pid":"893c3f527760cc2595ca6f7bf158d5153e1ed933","tid":2108762,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:15:36.000Z","msg":"傻閪，精神分裂炸"},{"pid":"da457d6821f1292060296ac60950b4859740c18e","tid":2108762,"uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:17:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yiwS80LpYbM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyiwS80LpYbM&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=b1e6bd81\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yiwS80LpYbM</a><br />\n<br />\nchristian rock 好嘢嚟"},{"pid":"b4108c125db53fe94e2356baef43e2c7eba67e30","tid":2108762,"uid":283215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:19:45.000Z","msg":"多謝你分享 想問下係祈完禱 佢會有指引 <br />\n<br />\n姐係無啦啦浮現個諗法？"},{"pid":"f618a285d96424e21262e426960e49389e9b3a0b","tid":2108762,"uid":222614,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:23:15.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">大衛對非利士人說：「你來攻擊我，是靠著刀槍和銅戟。我來攻擊你，是靠著萬軍之耶和華的名，就是你所怒罵帶領以色列軍隊的神。<br />\n</p><br />\n撒母耳記上 17:45<br />\n<br />\n同學們，緊靠住聖靈去克服每個難關吧！"},{"pid":"e82cfc88894762962f59ac3cdfe63b590d802986","tid":2108762,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4108c125db53fe94e2356baef43e2c7eba67e30","tid":2108762,"uid":283215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:19:45.000Z","msg":"多謝你分享 想問下係祈完禱 佢會有指引 <br />\n<br />\n姐係無啦啦浮現個諗法？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:33:55.000Z","msg":"我自己印象中好少係祈禱時有解決問題嘅 idea<br />\n<br />\n多數係遇到困難之後，同埋已經無曬辦法嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n聖靈就會係我思維入面唔知點樣令我無端端明白邊度出現問題，要點樣解決<br />\n<br />\n過程完全係被動，就好似有個人同自己講緊野咁<br />\n<br />\n最奇妙就係次次都 work，hallelujah!"},{"pid":"9413769dd929717ade55094b26eecaeb011365cc","tid":2108762,"uid":208640,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:38:17.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦 耶穌佬"},{"pid":"826294c0172c30373bff5325e51ae1bebc206948","tid":