們學習知識同技能，係屬世嘅事<br />\n<br />\n但係咩時候記起啲乜，就係屬靈嘅事<br />\n<br />\n凡係睇到 spiritual reality 嘅人都必須尋求基督耶穌，因為佢先係天國嘅主人<br />\n<br />\n無論靈界定世界，所有受造之物都不及耶穌，因為佢就係萬主之主，萬王之王"},{"pid":"c4b8cb2bbcfbe721e648a09861c21f39fa9c9e0e","tid":2108762,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T20:42:25.000Z","msg":"This is how things work as appointed by the most High God, whether you like it or not<br />\n<br />\nEveryone is a soul dwelling in a physical body<br />\n<br />\nEvery soul belongs to YEHOVAH God of Israel, our Creator<br />\n<br />\nEvery soul that sins shall die, but for those who are willing to repent, God our Father has prepared the salvation, and a way to eternal life <br />\n<br />\nMany people fabricate theories for souls to rely on, but none of them is capable to save us from dying in sin, being eternally separated from God<br />\n<br />\nEvery man made theory stands against the salvation from Jesus Christ, the only way to eternal life<br />\n<br />\nIn the last day, they shall not stand but all collapse because they are established by men, not by God<br />\n<br />\nAnd the kingdom of Jesus Christ shall stand forever and ever. Amen."},{"pid":"78b9e6fcc7a96246ef9c1a0be0596ff805f6f47f","tid":2108762,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T09:44:48.000Z","msg":"push ...."},{"pid":"0e0baaf27c3fb4b81cb6c6be3c18584fe18b2a8a","tid":2108762,"uid":360830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"80298309cf80f8d4681773f602b3c0079b1c24b5","tid":2108762,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:02:18.000Z","msg":"有時個腦實左，情況危急又唔知點<br />\n<br />\n聖靈就會畀指示我，係我思想入面提點我，話我知發生咩問題<br />\n<br />\n然後我跟住做，果然解決到問題<br />\n<br />\n已經發生過好多次，今日又有經歷<br />\n<br />\n我份人本身容易緊張同亂黎，試過無數次搞到一獲泡<br />\n<br />\n但學識遵從聖靈嘅指示後，每次遇到問題都會順利解決<br />\n<br />\n有聖靈嘅人會知我講咩<br />\n<br />\n願榮歸基督耶穌，amen!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4edaa71c65022bb20762fa6d51da342be34dfacf","tid":2108762,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T01:03:08.000Z","msg":"push ...."},{"pid":"0c9f5e22a9cbabfbc95ec0ed9076de25801ba636","tid":2108762,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:09:19.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><strong>physical reality vs spiritual reality</strong></p><br />\n<br />\n點解大衛可以贏到 goliath the philistine<br />\n<br />\n無論體形，武器定戰鬥經驗都明顯唔夠打，所以世人見到大衛單挑巨人都覺得輸梗<br />\n<br />\n世人同巨人見到嘅都係 physical reality，佢地亦係人生入面全力追求佢地所深信嘅致勝之道：<br />\nA 大／勁／強過 B，或者 A 嬴嘅因素多過 B，所以 A 會贏<br />\n<br />\n但上帝子民睇到嘅係 spiritual reality：<br />\n敵對上帝者必敗<br />\n<br />\n深明 spiritual reality，所以年少嘅大衛充滿信心，向住強敵呼喊：「你來攻擊我，是靠著刀槍和銅戟 (physical reality)。我來攻擊你，是靠著<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">萬軍之耶和華的名 (spiritual reality)，就是你所怒罵帶領以色列軍隊的神。</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n事後，只睇 physical reality 嘅人就會話：「原來石仔都可以打死巨人」，世人就係咁，用無數嘅神迹奇事入面去建立世人嘅理論，最終都係否認同無視 spiritual reality，所以唔肯信嘅人，見到神跡之後都係仍然唔願信<br />\n<br />\n家財萬貫，賺盡血錢，勢力龐大，權傾天下嘅人唔係降服係魔鬼之下咩？然而魔鬼一聽到至高者嘅聖名就驚慌逃離，依杖魔鬼勢力嘅人亦頓時失去依靠，上帝向佢地討債時佢地就分崩離析，無人能施救<br />\n<br />\n因為根據至高者嘅心意，用信心呼喊出佢嘅名係大有權柄，可以震撼靈界從而震撼物質界，為叫世人知道：萬軍之耶和華係帶領以色列軍隊嘅神，基督耶穌係帶領基督徒軍隊嘅神！Amen"}],"pinned":{"pid":"f618a285d96424e21262e426960e49389e9b3a0b","tid":2108762,"uid":222614,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:23:15.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">大衛對非利士人說：「你來攻擊我，是靠著刀槍和銅戟。我來攻擊你，是靠著萬軍之耶和華的名，就是你所怒罵帶領以色列軍隊的神。<br />\n</p><br />\n撒母耳記上 17:45<br />\n<br />\n同學們，緊靠住聖靈去克服每個難關吧！"}}